OL,3,CGregg Wallace axed from MasterChef
OL,4,Camid historical misconduct allegations
OL,6,FGregg Wallace will step away from
OL,7,Fpresenting MasterChef while complaints
OL,8,Fmade to the BBC from individuals about
OL,9,Fhistorical allegations of misconduct
OL,10,Fare investigated
OL,12,FThe Peckham born TV personality is
OL,13,F"committed to fully cooperating
OL,14,Fthroughout the process", a statement
OL,15,Ffrom the show's production company
OL,16,FBanijay UK to the PA news agency said.
OL,18,FWallace, 60, has presented MasterChef,
OL,19,Falongside John Torrode since 2005.
