OL,6,FThe statement said: "This week the BBC
OL,7,Freceived complaints from individuals
OL,8,Fin relation to historical allegations
OL,9,Fof misconduct while working with
OL,10,Fpresenter Gregg Wallace on one of our
OL,11,Fshows.
OL,13,F"Whilst these complainants have not
OL,14,Fraised the allegations directly with
OL,15,Four show producers or parent company
OL,16,FBanijay UK, we feel that it is
OL,17,Fappropriate to conduct an immediate,
OL,18,Fexternal review to fully and
OL,19,Fimpartially investigate.
