OL,6,F"Whilst these are historical
OL,7,Fallegations, incidences brought to our
OL,8,Fattention where these expectations are
OL,9,Fnot met, are thoroughly investigated
OL,10,Fand addressed appropriately."
OL,12,FThe statement added: "If anyone would
OL,13,Flike to talk to us or raise any issues
OL,14,For concerns, then they can contact
OL,15,Fspeakup@banijayuk.com in confidence."
OL,17,FA BBC spokesman said: "We take any
OL,18,Fissues that are raised with us
OL,19,Fseriously and we have robust processes
OL,20,Fin place to deal with them.
