OL,7,Fbehaviour which falls below the
OL,8,Fstandards expected by the BBC will not
OL,9,Fbe tolerated.
OL,11,F"Where an individual is contracted
OL,12,Fdirectly by an external production
OL,13,Fcompany we share any complaints or
OL,14,Fconcerns with that company and we will
OL,15,Falways support them when addressing
OL,16,Fthem."
